~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : show                                      ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : show <username> <text to show the user>

   This will show a user how to do what you type in the <text area>
   please note this is for helping other users.  And the wiz staff can
   see what you are showing each other.

   This helps you to help another user. You can use this to show them 
   how to use commands and other aspects of this talker.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
